{"tid":2229369,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[港產game] [Legendary Knight] 01 - 設施攻防戰 (無盡模式預告)","createTime":"2020-10-04T10:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T12:22:00.000Z","uid":332896,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa1354bb1ea8739d77fb5488a2a72a47d56b934","tid":2229369,"uid":332896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"小弟整既Legendary Knight (傳奇騎士) 將會係今個月內推出大型更新<br />\n依段時間好多謝各位巴絲支持 開發先至可以繼續進行<br />\n<br />\nV0.4.0將會包括新遊戲模式 - <span class=\"violet\">Endless mode</span><br />\n係度同大家透露一下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我整左一個新既地圖 作為Legendary Knight既總結<br />\nSize比之前既地圖更大 更有戰爭感覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfqmcP5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfqmcP5.png&h=55d5e53a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外玩家可以選擇擁有唔同特性既角色守城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1SLM8pO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1SLM8pO.png&h=f9353d7a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我會陸續upload多D細節同大家分享<br />\n不過今次講左設施攻防戰先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSG4U0A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSG4U0A.png&h=8afa9b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">短片</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=397186467974271\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D397186467974271&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7y9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=fa6d47fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=397186467974271</a><br />\n[size=5]01 - 設施攻防戰[/size=4]<br />\n為左提高生存時間 <br />\n玩家可以適當地分配兵力及時間 <br />\n重奪城鎮內的設施<br />\n<br />\n設施有三個:<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">軍壘</span>: 自動生產民兵 作為西面城牆的第一道防線<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">兵營</span>: 為範圍內的友軍回復生命值<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">工房</span>: 為所有設施及雕像進行修理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OP5UxVg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOP5UxVg.png&h=8d1facf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩家可以親自衝鋒<br />\n亦可指揮守衛進行攻擊<br />\n各個設施都有相當重要的作用<br />\n保護已佔領的設施也是戰略重點之一<br />\n<br />\n下次再講 D野未整好 show唔到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n============================<br />\nLegendary Knight 傳奇騎士<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35vgpUz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35vgpUz&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7y9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=0f93a70e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35vgpUz</a><br />\n<br />\n大木遊戲研究所<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/okigamelab/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fokigamelab%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7y9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=baa45cee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/okigamelab/</a><br />\n<br />\n買杯咖啡俾大木<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buymeacoffee.com/okigamelab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buymeacoffee.com%2Fokigamelab&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7y9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=261671f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.buymeacoffee.com/okigamelab</a>"},{"pid":"8446ed30a48f8e26161a321996b13b7f3ba5163a","tid":2229369,"uid":34006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"support<br />\n係時候玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b29cb758d3262ab7d37fd03213c59c3e59b24c4","tid":2229369,"uid":332896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8446ed30a48f8e26161a321996b13b7f3ba5163a","tid":2229369,"uid":34006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"support<br />\n係時候玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"未出未出 趕工中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9564f950226761cef474a41231ab6aee171b95b6","